  I'm not trying to change the subject at hand, I'm only trying to give all ideas a fair chance.  Though it can be dangerous to be open-minded, it sure as hell can be just as dangerous being close-minded too.    <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ubrutas222.showPublicProfile?language=EN>brutas222</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 171<br> <font color=#E9D756>(2/13/02 10:00:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=269.topic&index=216>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> re: Expectations and consequences of God</span><hr size=1> <br>
