<br>
OK, looks like I have responded to all your points. Please let me know if I missed anything.<br>
<br>
Finally, I want to share something with you Cendan. A senior pastor of mine who recently died and joined God in heaven asked me when I was 20 years old (trust me that was a long time ago!) the following question:<br>
<br>
&quot;How do you like your steak? Do you like it cooked or Frozen?&quot; He asked me the question after I had handed out tracks to the local Seventh Day Adventists as they were leaving their church. I was so on fire with my doctrine I had forgotten one thing. I responded to the question that I liked my steak cook. My pastor told me I handed out &quot;frozen steaks&quot; that day.<br>
<br>
